documentation:
ListAddFields uses to transform record by adding an ids from list object field to one list.

input:
{
     ...,
    "updates": [{
    {
    "id": "some id",...
    },
    {
    "id": "some id",...
    },
    ...
    }]
}

output:
{
     ...,
    "updates_ids": ["some id", "some id", ...]
    "updates": [{
    {
    "id": "some id",...
    },
    {
    "id": "some id",...
    },
    ...
    }]
}
